<!doctype html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>常见问题</title>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<link href="../../css/mui.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<link href="../../css/leWan.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<link href="../../fonts/iconfont.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<style type="text/css">
			
		body {
			padding: 0;
			margin: 0;
		}
		.contentBox{
			overflow: hidden;
		}
		.header{
			height: 100%;
		}
		.header>img{
			width: 100%;
			display: block;
		}
		.mui-table-view:before{
			height: 0;
		}
		.questionBox{
			min-height: 100vh;
			background-color: #FFFFFF;
		}
		.title{
			padding-top: 0.5rem;
			padding-left: 0.56rem;
			padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
			font-size: 0.426rem;
			color: #333333;
			font-weight: 500;
		}
		.mui-media>div:nth-child(1){
			font-size: 0.373rem;
			font-size: 500;
			color: #333333;
		}
		.isShow{
			height: 0;
			display: none;
			font-size: 0.35rem;
			font-size: 200;
			color: #999999;
			margin-top: 0.2rem;
		}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div class="contentBox">
			<div class="header">
				<img src="../../img/reservationCenter/reservationCenter2.png"/>
			</div>
			<div class="questionBox">
				<div class="title">常见问题</div>
				<ul class="mui-table-view">
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell mui-media">
						<div>1：购买商品后电子码丢失如何找回 ？</div>
						<div class="isShow">进入“乐玩联盟”商城首页，找到我的个人中心，查看我的订单，点击选择该商品订单详情即可看见电子码 。</div>
					</li>
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell mui-media">
						<div>2：购买需提前预约产品怎么预约？</div>
						<div class="isShow">进入“乐玩联盟”首页，点击底部菜单“预约中心”，进入页面后选择消费日期，进行预约即可。</div>
					</li>
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell mui-media">
						<div>3：预约后想更换或取消预约日期在哪里修改呢？</div>
						<div class="isShow">联系客服微信，出示所购买的姓名，手机号码，产品，数量以及更换预约日期沟通即可。</br>（注：只针对可取消预约商品，取消规则以该商品详情为准。）</div>
					</li>
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell mui-media">
						<div>4：购买商品后发现不适合不想要可以退换吗 ？</div>
						<div class="isShow">所有抢购商品购买后一律不退不换，以商品详情为准。</div>
					</li>
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell mui-media">
						<div>5：邮寄商品多久能到呢？</div>
						<div class="isShow">邮寄商品本地区域1-2天，外地3-5天（视商品始发地-目的地，以及节假日是否会延迟具体情况为准）。</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<script src="../../plugins/flexible.js"></script>
		<script src="../../plugins/jquery-2.1.4.js"></script>
		<script src="../../plugins/vue.js"></script>
		<script src="../../js/mui.min.js"></script>
		<script src="../../plugins/serverApi.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			$(document).ready(function() {
				mui('body').on('tap','.mui-media',function(){
					var index = $(this).index();
					log(index)
					$('.isShow').css({'height':'0','display':'none'});
					$('.isShow').eq(index).css({'height':'auto','display':'block'})
				})
			});
		</script>
	</body>

</html>